snippet.title: TIMBERWOLVES at LAKERS | NBA PRESEASON FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 4, 2024
snippet.description:
Never miss a moment with the latest news, trending stories and highlights to bring you closer to your favorite players and teams.
Download now: https://link.nba.com/NBAYouTube

The Minnesota Timberwolves defeat the Los Angeles Lakers 124-97. Josh Minott led the Timberwolves with 22 points and 8 rebounds while rookies Rob Dillingham (21 points, 4 assists) and Terrance Shannon Jr (14 points, 4 rebounds, 5 assists) combine for 35 points in the win. Donte DiVincenzo put up 11 points (3/3 3PT FG) for the Timberwolves. Austin Reaves tallied 16 points, 5 rebounds and 7 assists for the Lakers while Dalton Knecht totaled 16 points, 3 rebounds in his preseason debut. The Timberwolves move to 1-0 in the preseason while the Lakers fall to 0-1.

- To edit, I use Final Cut Pro X. To film, I use a Canon EOS R8 and my iPhone. To record my voice, I use a RODE VideoMic Go.

- No
What do I do with my Lego builds after a video is finished?
- I have to take them apart to use for the next video
